====Definitions====
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# to [[ask]]; to [[ask]] for; to [[request]]
#: {{zh-x|請 幾 日 假{gaa3}|to '''request''' several days off ({{zh-m|請假|tr=-}})|C}}
#: {{zh-x|請 你 不要 把 我 當{dànɡ} 傻子{zi}。|Please don't treat me like a fool.}}
#: {{zh-x|我 請 他 幫 我 買 東西{xi}。|I asked him to buy something for me.}}
#* {{zh-x|^陳 ^恆 弒 其 君，請 討 之。|Chen Heng has slain his sovereign. I '''beg''' that you will undertake to punish him.|ref=Analects}}
#* {{zh-x|請 子 奉 之，以 主 社稷。||ref=Zuozhuan}}
#* {{zh-x|^羿 請 不死 之 藥 於 ^西王母，^姮{héng}娥 竊 以 奔 月|{{w|Hou Yi}} '''asked for''' the medicine of immortality from the {{w|Queen Mother of the West}}, [and] {{w|Chang'e}} stole it in order to escape to the moon|ref=Huainanzi}}
## [[kindly]] allow me to...
##* {{zh-x|^顏 ^淵 曰：「^回 雖 不 敏，請 事 斯 語 矣。」|Yan Yuan then said, "Though I am deficient in intelligence and vigor, I will make it my business to practice this lesson."|ref=Analects}}
##* {{zh-x|王 好{hào}戰，請 以 戰 喻。|Your majesty is fond of war - '''let me''' take an illustration from war.|ref=Mencius}}
# to [[ask]]
# to [[greet]]; to [[ask]] how someone is
#: {{zh-co|請安|to pay respect (to someone senior)}}
#* {{zh-x|陸 生 往 請，直 入 坐，而 ^陳 丞相 方 深念，不時 見 ^陸 生。||ref=Shiji}}
# to [[invite]]; to [[treat]] (to a [[meal]], etc.)
#: {{zh-co|不請自來|to turn up without being invited}}
#: {{zh-x|如果 你 得閒{haan4}，我 想 請 你 飲茶。|If you are free, I would like to ask you out for [[yum cha]].|C}}
# to [[hire]]
#: {{zh-x|請 工人|'''hire''' workers.}}
#: {{zh-x|佢 冇 錢{cin4-2} 請 律師。|He does not have the money to '''hire''' a lawyer.|C}}
# to [[carry]] or [[bring]] (a [[sacred]] or [[respectable]] [[thing]])
#: {{zh-co|請 神|}}
#: {{zh-x|展 護衛，請 聖旨！|Royal Guard Zhan, '''bring out''' the royal edict!}}
# [[please]]; [[kindly]]
#: {{zh-x|請 稍候。|Just a moment, please}}
#: {{zh-co|請 坐|Please be seated.|C}}
# {{lb|zh|dated}} to [[buy]] [[holy]] [[sacrificial]] [[object]]s {{gl|such as joss sticks, candles, paper horses, etc.}}
